snippet.title: Infinity Strash: DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai - Pre-Order Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Pre-order Infinity Strash: DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai for Nintendo Switch

When the Dark Lord is revived, Dai begins his quest to become a true hero! Assemble the Disciples of Avan, discover an unescapable fate, and defeat the Dark Army in Infinity Strash: DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai!  

#DQDai #InfinityStrash #NintendoSwitch
